<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Mappy</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-28 20:11:45</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yes, the first cap that you get for turning in the skins only (ac 4, plus 10 cha) can be worn by multiple races...I didnt check which ones specifically but it seemed like there were about 8 or so listed.  I imagine small and medium...this is a good quest in my opinion, and not too rough if you can port around a bit.  I can verify that only Bull alligators in Innothule swamp drop the alligator skin, and the area around the tower seems like a good spot for them.  Another cool thing about this quest is that the Deputy who gives it declares that you are a member of the Leatherfoot Raider squad, the elite guard of Rivervale hehe...no real game impact as far as I know, but a cool thing to put in your text screen.</font></td></tr></table>
