<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Raynn Fahling</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-25 13:22:04</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white><BR>
Finally... )  i found out how to get the quest... after wasting one of my skins by just giving to the halfling guy.<BR>
<BR>
At the very top of castle (the one with the bank) past all the other guys and the window is the last nook.  this is the guy with the quest.<BR>
<BR>
You say to him:  I am petitioning.  then  he says "you are a mess. where are you [from]?"  you then say  I am from rivervale.<BR>
<BR>
he then gives you the quest. )<BR>
<BR>
i had 2 skins left (the bulls dropped the gator skins, shark in efp, bought polars from newbies in halas, grizzly i bought from vendor in wc)<BR>
<BR>
Got a dirk off of dvinn.  Now i have a full-on hlf only cap AND a 10cha head item for my trade skill learning woodelf druid as well ).<BR>
<BR>
Good hunting. <BR>
<BR>
Raynn Fahling<BR>
29 druid<BR>
Brell</font></td></tr></table>
